Alison Moore | Podcast
</a>
</h2>
<h4 class="dnd_post-card_author">
<a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/alison-moore/">Alison Moore</a> & <a class="contributor-link" href="https://granta.com/contributor/john-freeman/">John Freeman</a>
</h4>
<p class="dnd_post-card_text">
Alison Moore spoke to John Freeman about the experience of being shortlisted for the Man Booker Prize, why her characters often find themselves enclosed in a memory and writing short.
</p>
